name: Expovision Roller Banner
description:
Roller banners have always been one of the most popular promotional materials available, and the Expovision is our most popular product within this range.

This lightweight roller banner is our value option and is perfect for any trade show or exhibition event.

  • Available in 4 different widths: 850mm, 1000mm, 1200mm and 1500mm
  • Standard height of 2000mm across all widths
  • 2 twist out feet add stability
  • Compact lightweight base
  • Single sided banner
  • Includes a Carry Case

name: Bannerbow Arch Expo & Event
description:
Whether you are participating in a roadshow or a event, Bannerbow products can inject that little bit of extra flair you are looking for. The event arches are flexible and can easily be moved from an entrance to an exhibition stand. One product which offers many possibilities.

Our event arches are perfect for exhibitions or as a flexible part of an interior. Our first new product in 2018, Bannerbow Backdrop offers a perfect set for exhibitions and events.

  • Frame Material-fiberglass
  • Foot material - Indoor Aluminium Base or Outdoor Steel Base
  • Printed on 115gsm Knitted Polyester
  • Colour of base - black
  • Depth - 1000mm
  • Transport trolley bag included
  • Indoor or Outdoor use
